{"tid":630144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"節目惡剪變衰人　小豬嬲爆要求公開道歉","createTime":"2018-04-15T10:28:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-16T03:38:08.000Z","uid":89543,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"72c4f6b7980e7e751066ae0f265559c54d91dde2","tid":630144,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T10:28:36.000Z","msg":"台灣歌手羅志祥（小豬）為內地選秀真人騷《這！就是街舞》擔任明星隊長，節目自播出以嚟回響亦好大，近呢兩期仲不斷有網友留言批評節目組喺剪輯上，刻意塑造小豬成為「出言不遜」、「欺負他人」嘅形象，亦令小豬成為網民攻擊對象。 <br />\n<br />\n就呢一件事，小豬今日都有喺微博發文表心達心情：「上一期的剪輯播出　我被罵了　這黑鍋我背了　我忍了　但這一期的剪輯更是過分　前後剪輯顛倒　導致觀眾對我們的誤解　這次我忍不下去了　我們四位隊長　還有所有舞者對節目的認真付出　也希望可以得到節目對我們的尊重！ 」<br />\n<br />\n而小豬工作室今日亦透過微博發聲明，要求節目組公開道歉，聲明全文如下： <br />\n「羅志祥先生在與《這！就是街舞》節目的合作中，從始至終抱著（着）認真負責的態度全力配合節目的各項工作，工作室也一直積極友善地與節目方進行溝通。 <br />\n出道24年，羅志祥先生視舞蹈為生命。讓更多人了解街舞、喜歡街舞，讓優秀的舞者為更多人熟知，是羅志祥先生參加節目的初衷。 <br />\n我們很遺憾，在最近兩期的節目當中，節目方罔顧現場錄製的實際情況，在成片中刪減了羅志祥先生符合情理與邏輯的行為與表現，節目成片帶有強烈的情緒誤導，由此帶來的負面輿論已經嚴重影響到藝人的名譽，造成了巨大的傷害。 <br />\n我們無法得知這樣的剪輯用意幾何，但我們強烈譴責這樣故意製造矛盾，引導不良情緒，違背藝人初心，罔顧藝人配合的行為。 <br />\n鑑於此，羅志祥先生及工作室要求節目方公開道歉，並妥善處理近兩期節目剪輯所帶來的問題，給藝人也給觀眾一個交代。認真是對舞台的尊重，這種尊重不應該因任何理由被褻瀆。 <br />\n以舞為魂，以誠立身。 <br />\n初心不改，方得始終。」"},{"pid":"b9482294dab8650eb8cb4be39e2db916636633f2","tid":630144,"uid":3017,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T10:30:15.000Z","msg":"不用分那麼細<br />\n大家都是中國人丫嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9552ddf17af8cb6992b761cf2b9cacb10b5bd2fe","tid":630144,"uid":37136,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T10:31:36.000Z","msg":"支那豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb27453d8a5e88ecc1fc6bce1cd339660396a7a7","tid":630144,"uid":693,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T10:33:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不用分那麼細啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53aa8409d93a2401de2c79a0d28af6966e66cb68","tid":630144,"uid":10757,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T10:38:50.000Z","msg":"吓! 上得依d節目 預左架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf4217f293e2441434ce788b6cdbb4d18dcbdfd4","tid":630144,"uid":129521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T11:06:17.000Z","msg":"有人逼佢搵人仔？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54bdd74930548f34bd9b84ee14b924401fdf6b0d","tid":630144,"uid":67500,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T11:08:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/190819_452e25fdc85ec988fd3fb98d4936a9d4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F190819_452e25fdc85ec988fd3fb98d4936a9d4.gif&h=dafe06bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/190830_bbb458b8df76898125d755ed9c28acac.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F190830_bbb458b8df76898125d755ed9c28acac.gif&h=5f2251eb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e1fdeef21b2b782da6fa10a2af4e435c1ca9947","tid":630144,"uid":50060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"54bdd74930548f34bd9b84ee14b924401fdf6b0d","tid":630144,"uid":67500,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T11:08:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/190819_452e25fdc85ec988fd3fb98d4936a9d4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F190819_452e25fdc85ec988fd3fb98d4936a9d4.gif&h=dafe06bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018